text.section:
A local government that authorizes financing through assessments as part of a program established pursuant to KRS 65.205 to 65.209 shall file written notice of each assessment in the real property records of the county in which the property is located. This notice shall include:
The amount of the assessment;
The legal description of the real property;
The name of each owner of record of the real property; and
A reference to the statutory assessment lien provided under this section.
